        "TileImage": "$($repository b624bd85-96f7-45b9-93ff-92a05e77accc).Image",
        "Description": "Caruso needs no Doctor Oscar. The only reason he is being distracted is that woman with a hat who is wandering around the plaza in front of his mansion. She always reminds him of his mother, so he wants her to be as dead as his mother too. Caruso also demands to kill her just like he killed mother. It is unlikely we will ever have a chance to kill her with a pillow, so you need to improvise 47. Give the poor man a real therapy.",
